{"type":"message","id":"b3805141","parentId":"a98e7b76","timestamp":"2026-05-07T14:28:34.772Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o5ern71yvaf2_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializing skill: ufo-gpt-image-gen\n   Location: /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills\n   Resources: references\n\n[OK] Created skill directory: /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-gpt-image-gen\n[OK] Created SKILL.md\n[OK] Created references/\n\n[OK] Skill 'ufo-gpt-image-gen' initialized successfully at /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-gpt-image-gen\n\nNext steps:\n1. Edit SKILL.md to complete the TODO items and update the description\n2. Add resources to scripts/, references/, and assets/ as needed\n3. Run the validator when ready to check the skill structure"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":49,"aggregated":"Initializing skill: ufo-gpt-image-gen\n   Location: /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills\n   Resources: references\n\n[OK] Created skill directory: /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-gpt-image-gen\n[OK] Created SKILL.md\n[OK] Created references/\n\n[OK] Skill 'ufo-gpt-image-gen' initialized successfully at /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-gpt-image-gen\n\nNext steps:\n1. Edit SKILL.md to complete the TODO items and update the description\n2. Add resources to scripts/, references/, and assets/ as needed\n3. Run the validator when ready to check the skill structure","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778164114772}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e7e0a56","parentId":"b3805141","timestamp":"2026-05-07T14:28:58.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the skill is initialized. Now let me write the SKILL.md and a references file with the detailed workflow.\n","thinkingSignature":"77fa3e30bab192d32019c0dc5242dae9e212e5f60b15a6c463a7618651248b24"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_66l4l19f1wzm_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: ufo-gpt-image-gen\ndescription: Generate 3D prop/object images via ChatGPT Custom GPT using Chrome CDP automation. Use when boss wants to create images for 3D modeling workflow. Triggers: (1) Boss asks to generate an image, (2) Boss provides a Thai prompt for a prop/object, (3) Using ChatGPT to create images for 3D printing/modeling, (4) any image generation request that uses the Custom GPT at chatgpt.com/g/g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1. This skill replaces manual ChatGPT Web usage — it runs gpt_background_image.py which handles Chrome CDP connection, prompt submission via DOM, dual verification gates (technical + Moondream vision), and auto-cleanup.\n---\n\n# ufo-gpt-image-gen\n\nGenerate images via ChatGPT Custom GPT for 3D modeling using Chrome CDP automation.\n\n## Quick Usage\n\n```bash\nbash \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Desktop/Work Auto/ufo-gpt-image-gen/generate_bg.sh\" \"ร้านขายผ้าสีสันสดใส\"\n```\n\nOutput: PNG saved to `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป 3D\\`\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. **Start Chrome CDP** via `start_chrome_bg.ps1` (verifies port 9222 is listening)\n2. **Run `gpt_background_image.py`** — connects Chrome, submits prompt via DOM, waits for generated image\n3. **Technical Gate** — image URL must be `backend-api/estuary/content`, resolution >= 1000x700, size >= 300KB\n4. **Vision Gate** — Moondream describes image, qwen2.5:3b judges match (confidence >= 0.75)\n5. **Save & cleanup** — PNG to output folder, delete `runtime 🏃💨` temp folder\n\n## Key Paths\n\n| Purpose | Windows Path |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Output folder** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\รูป 3D\\` |\n| **Tool root** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-gpt-image-gen\\` |\n| **Runtime temp** | `C:\\Users\\Apinan\\Desktop\\Work Auto\\ufo-gpt-image-gen\\runtime 🏃💨\\` |\n| **Chrome CDP** | `http://[::1]:9222` |\n| **GPT URL** | `https://chatgpt.com/g/g-69e8e8cd64fc81918d57af195508f4b1` |\n\n## Scripts\n\n| Script | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `generate_bg.sh` | Main entry — call from WSL/Linux |\n| `start_chrome_bg.ps1` | Start/verify Chrome remote debugging |\n| `gpt_background_image.py` | Core automation (CDP connect → DOM input → verify → save) |\n| `verify_image_moondream.py` | Single image verification tool |\n\n## Verification Gates\n\nSee [references/verification.md](references/verification.md) for full details.\n\n## Notes\n\n- No real keyboard/mouse — all via CDP/DOM only\n- Runtime temp folder is auto-deleted after completion\n- Rejects thumbnails, previews, avatars automatically\n- Only ChatGPT estuary content URLs are accepted","path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ufo-gpt-image-gen/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":313,"output":804,"cacheRead":37568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38685,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778164114773,"responseId":"064bd4944ab5927d9417478fd103d1e3"}}
