{"type":"message","id":"0c132172","parentId":"ed5d555f","timestamp":"2026-05-07T15:25:49.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The openai provider has an empty apiKey. That's why it can't check. The owner needs to set a real OpenAI API key to check usage limits.\n\nLet me be honest with the boss.\n","thinkingSignature":"252891facbbe5461506e0619f169755c7119921d37cb73e9873d187d0e2f2ff7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 ตอบตรงๆ เจ้านาย\n\n---\n\n**ปัญหา:** `openai` provider ไม่มี API key — ว่างเปล่า\n\n```json\n\"openai\": {\n  \"apiKey\": \"\",      ← ว่างไปแล้ว\n  \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.openai.com/v1\"\n}\n```\n\nเลยเช็ค usage limit ไม่ได้\n\n---\n\n**อยากเช็คได้?** ต้องใส่ OpenAI API key จริงๆ\n\nเจ้านายมี API key ที่ platform.openai.com ไหม? ถ้ามี บอกมาได้เลย (เริ่มต้นด้วย `sk-...`) แล้วจะ setup ให้เช็ค usage limit ได้ทันทีครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":184,"output":297,"cacheRead":66208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778167543547,"responseId":"064be1f8fdd4f89b83008c3ed2f94683"}}
