{"type":"message","id":"993026e2","parentId":"eb721b25","timestamp":"2026-05-07T15:36:26.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No GPU on this machine (WSL/Linux). Let me just report CPU and RAM.","thinkingSignature":"76b4388ef2fef96d5d9213ea613398e3e5641527c6d5b016c721106d31ee82c4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🖥️ **ดึงมาแล้วครับ**\n\n```\n🖥️ CPU: 4.8%\n💾 RAM: 4.0Gi / 23Gi (17%)\n```\n\n---\n\nไม่มี GPU ในเครื่องนี้ (WSL2) ถ้าเจ้านายอยากให้ดู GPU ด้วย ต้องรันบน Windows หรือเครื่องที่มี GPU card จริงๆ ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":166,"cacheRead":66272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778168178742,"responseId":"064be475aca05951207b1c393908ad71"}}
