{"type":"message","id":"9cce549c","parentId":"ddba9253","timestamp":"2026-05-07T15:37:35.829Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The script works. Let me show the output preview.\n\nNow let me create a .ps1 for Windows users and a .sh for Linux/WSL users.","thinkingSignature":"4769ca38e2efb76cd9d6ce3d5274742b302d1472ed2fc9f213f39f3a35fd6cae"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nรันได้แล้วครับ! ลองดู:\n\n```\n  CPU  100.0% [████████████████████]\n  RAM  17.0% [███░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░]  4.0G / 23.0G\n  2026-05-07 22:37:23\n```\n\nพร้อมกันนั้น title bar ก็ update ด้วย:\n```\nCPU   4.8% | RAM  17.0% | GPU N/A | 22:37:23\n```\n\n---\n\n## วิธีรัน\n\n```bash\n# WSL/Linux\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/sysmon.py\n\n# ปรับความเร็ว (วินาที)\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/sysmon.py 0.5   # ครึ่มวินาที update ครั้ง\n```\n\n---\n\n## บน Windows PowerShell\n\n```powershell\n# หรือสร้าง shortcut แบบไม่ต้องเปิด window ใหม่\n```\n\nจะให้ทำ shortcut icon บน desktop ด้วยไหมครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":314,"output":355,"cacheRead":67776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68445,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778168245763,"responseId":"064be4b8c44e4c8a83570085c0ebb1fc"}}
