{"type":"message","id":"a13effe6","parentId":"dd626c84","timestamp":"2026-05-07T15:48:26.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The window handle is 0 because it's using pythonw (no window) and tkinter overlay may be a different window. Let me try to move it to monitor 2 via SetWindowPos or similar.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use EnumDisplayMonitors to find monitor 2 bounds, then move the tkinter window there.","thinkingSignature":"ccca5a652082c92fe45842266c5f0fac270685acf615cbe3c464c220512d8b75"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tbobefvyks6j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"\"/mnt/c/Windows/System32/WindowsPowerShell/v1.0/powershell.exe\" -Command \"\nAdd-Type @'\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\nusing System.Drawing;\n\npublic class Monitors {\n    [DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")]\n    public static extern bool EnumDisplayMonitors(IntPtr hdc, IntPtr rc, MonitorEnumProc cb, IntPtr lParam);\n    public delegate bool MonitorEnumProc(IntPtr hMonitor, IntPtr hdc, ref RECT lprc, IntPtr dwData);\n    [StructLayout(LayoutKind.Sequential)]\n    public struct RECT { public int left; public int top; public int right; public int bottom; }\n    public static int index = 0;\n    public static int index2Left = 0, index2Top = 0, index2Right = 0, index2Bottom = 0;\n}\n'@\n\n# Also need to create the monitors array\n\\$monArr = @()\n\\$monitors = @()\n\n\\$callback = [Monitors+MonitorEnumProc]{\n    param(\\$h,\\$hc,\\$rc,\\$d)\n    \\$r = \\$rc -as [Monitors+RECT]\n    \\$monitors += [PSCustomObject]@{Left=\\$r.left;Top=\\$r.top;Right=\\$r.right;Bottom=\\$r.bottom}\n    return \\$true\n}\n\n\\$type = @'\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\npublic class M2 {\n    [DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")] public static extern bool EnumDisplayMonitors(IntPtr hdc, IntPtr rc, MonCb cb, IntPtr d);\n    public delegate bool MonCb(IntPtr h, IntPtr hdc, ref RECT r, IntPtr d);\n    [StructLayout(LayoutKind.Sequential)] public struct RECT { public int left,top,right,bottom; }\n    public static System.Collections.ArrayList Rects = System.Collections.ArrayList.Synchronized(new System.Collections.ArrayList());\n    public static bool Callback(IntPtr h, IntPtr hdc, ref RECT r, IntPtr d) {\n        Rects.Add(new RECT{left=r.left,top=r.top,right=r.right,bottom=r.bottom});\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n'@\nAdd-Type \\$type -ReferencedAssemblies System.Drawing\n[M2]::EnumDisplayMonitors([IntPtr]::Zero, [IntPtr]::Zero, [M2+MonCb],[IntPtr]::Zero) | Out-Null\n[M2]::Rects | ForEach-Object { \\$_ | ConvertTo-Json }\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":191,"output":640,"cacheRead":83296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84127,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778168877417,"responseId":"064be7305ef5deef7f8d18502560e888"}}
