{"type":"message","id":"a52e9a43","parentId":"25a411de","timestamp":"2026-05-07T16:07:47.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to check the actual lines and see what changed. The H changed from 130 to 135 and W from 240 to 260. Let me read the file again and fix the position. I think it's just a size change, not position. Let me verify by reading the relevant lines more carefully.\n\nActually, looking at it more carefully - the issue the user reported is \"ตำแหน่งถูกย้าย\" (position was moved) - this is likely because the window size changed from 240x130 to 260x135, which affects where the top-right corner lands. I need to fix the position to account for the new size.\n\nNew size: W=260, H=135\n\n\nSo the right side of monitor 2 is at x = 1536 + 1536 - 20 - 260 = 2792, and the top is at y = 20. Let me apply that adjustment.","thinkingSignature":"3282bae56b8d05a7113fd2e7925fbb51cd09eaeac02f1272dda995c9089b77cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wd3pznr9vxfx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '100,106p' /home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/sysmon.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":277,"output":243,"cacheRead":109824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110344,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778170061501,"responseId":"064bebd03e8172f54bf50ab5bc335ff9"}}
