{"type":"message","id":"5c3b9ee7","parentId":"efda2624","timestamp":"2026-05-07T17:07:51.222Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lmlx70xndlvr_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.6 (c97b9f7)\n⏱️ Uptime: gateway 1m 33s · system 1d 12h\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n🔄 Fallbacks: ollama-pay/deepseek-v4-pro:cloud, ollama-pay/gemini-3-flash-preview:cloud, ollama-pay/qwen3.5:397b-cloud\n🧮 Tokens: 3.1k in / 439 out\n🗄️ Cache: 48% hit · 59k cached, 59k new\n📚 Context: 59k/200k (30%) · 🧹 Compactions: 1\n📊 Usage: 5h 41% left ⏱2h 52m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:telegram:direct:robberzaz • updated just now\n⚙️ Execution: direct · Runtime: OpenClaw Pi Default · Think: medium · elevated\n🪢 Queue: steer (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:telegram:direct:robberzaz","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.6 (c97b9f7)\n⏱️ Uptime: gateway 1m 33s · system 1d 12h\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n🔄 Fallbacks: ollama-pay/deepseek-v4-pro:cloud, ollama-pay/gemini-3-flash-preview:cloud, ollama-pay/qwen3.5:397b-cloud\n🧮 Tokens: 3.1k in / 439 out\n🗄️ Cache: 48% hit · 59k cached, 59k new\n📚 Context: 59k/200k (30%) · 🧹 Compactions: 1\n📊 Usage: 5h 41% left ⏱2h 52m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:telegram:direct:robberzaz • updated just now\n⚙️ Execution: direct · Runtime: OpenClaw Pi Default · Think: medium · elevated\n🪢 Queue: steer (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778173671221}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ec229d0","parentId":"5c3b9ee7","timestamp":"2026-05-07T17:07:56.753Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is back and `Think: medium` is now set. MiniMax-M2.7 should now be using thinking/reasoning. Let me confirm this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"a97dade2b3e09ba159d83b7a5f34fc7dc27cc63c14c613e37a97a9f5ede5446e"},{"type":"text","text":"🧑🏼‍💻 **ได้แล้วครับเจ้านาย!** Gateway กลับมาแล้ว — ตอนนี้ `Think: medium` ✅\n\nMiniMax-M2.7 จะใช้ reasoning แล้ว ลองถามคำถามยาว ๆ ดูได้เลยครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35418,"output":153,"cacheRead":24205,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59776,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778173671225,"responseId":"064bf9e874509e88817e173be59f4d06"}}
