{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1060942816\",\n  \"message_id\": \"6814\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"sender\": \"▫️\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-08 00:12 GMT+7\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"▫️ (1060942816)\",\n  \"id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"name\": \"▫️\",\n  \"username\": \"robberzaz\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"c572cd5b","parentId":"cb57e887","timestamp":"2026-05-07T17:12:45.476Z"}
