{"type":"message","id":"2e01aee9","parentId":"a26ae870","timestamp":"2026-05-07T17:23:05.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there's a way to force/use git to track or manage the SocratiCode MCP server version. They want to know how to control which version of SocratiCode is being used.\n\nLooking at the config, SocratiCode is installed via `npx -y socraticode` which means it always uses the latest version from npm each time. There's no version pinning.\n\nThe user might want to:\n1. Pin a specific version of SocratiCode\n2. Or know if git can help track/manage this\n\nSince SocratiCode is an MCP server that runs via npx, git itself can't really manage it directly. \n\nThe real issue is that we're relying on the npm package `socraticode-mcp` or the npm package `socraticode` without version control, and since it's invoked through npx without a locked version, there's no way to guarantee which version gets installed or used.","thinkingSignature":"df866663343dafbda2ec2d8b679a8fec7ef7733f513447794d5b9914e2e058a2"},{"type":"text","text":"หลัก ๆ แล้ว SocratiCode รันผ่าน `npx -y socraticode` ซึ่งดึง latest ทุกครั้ง ไม่ได้ lock version ไว้\n\n**วิธีบังคับ version:**\n\n**1. กำหนด version แบบ fix ใน config:**\n```json\n\"mcpServers\": {\n  \"socraticode\": {\n    \"command\": \"npx\",\n    \"args\": [\"-y\", \"socraticode@1.8.8\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**2. หรือติดตั้ง local แล้วรันเอง:**\n```bash\nnpm install -g socraticode@1.8.8\n# แล้วเปลี่ยน command เป็นใช้ local binary\n```\n\n**3. ใช้ git?** — git เองไม่ได้ควบคุม MCP server version โดยตรง แต่เก็บ config ได้\n\n---\n\nจะให้ผมเปลี่ยน config ให้ lock เป็น `v1.8.8` เลยไหมครับ? ป้องกัน случайна updating แบบที่ไม่ได้ control 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":545,"cacheRead":24250,"cacheWrite":62999,"totalTokens":87964,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778174569844,"responseId":"064bfd6d04e77e1cb6ebb68cbd394061"}}
