{"type":"message","id":"0b81a2a1","parentId":"0c62d4d6","timestamp":"2026-05-07T17:49:25.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"ใช้ gpuไม่ได้เหรอ\" - meaning \"can't use GPU?\"\n\nLooking at the original setup - RTX 3060 8GB + 28GB RAM. The user is asking why can't we use GPU for this.\n\nActually the setup DOES use GPU - the `--n-gpu-layers 999` means it loads as many layers as possible to GPU. The MoE experts that can't fit in 8GB VRAM get offloaded to CPU via `--n-cpu-moe 38`.\n\nSo GPU is being used! But because it's only 8GB, it can't fit all the MoE experts. That's why `--n-cpu-moe 38` is needed - to delegate some experts to CPU.\n\n\nThe user might be confused thinking only CPU is being used, but the 8GB VRAM constraint means we have to split the MoE experts between GPU and CPU - GPU handles what it can fit while the rest goes to CPU.","thinkingSignature":"806ce96582ef93c4675f0c06506227733a6a114fb4bd2d6300a7263eec7d737a"},{"type":"text","text":"ใช้ GPU ได้ครับ! แต่ **8GB มันไม่พอ** สำหรับ Qwen3.6 35B ทั้งหมด\n\n## 🎮 สิ่งที่เกิดขึ้นจริง:\n\n```\nRTX 3060 8GB VRAM\n │\n ├─ โหลดได้แค่ ~30% ของโมเดล → GPU\n │\n └─ ที่เหลือ (~70%) → ใช้ CPU แทนผ่าน --n-cpu-moe\n```\n\n## ⚡ ทำไมต้องแบ่ง:\n\n| | 3060 8GB |\n|--|----------|\n| Qwen3.6 35B โหลดทั้งหมด | ต้องการ ~70GB |\n| VRAM ได้แค่ | 8GB |\n| ที่ขาด | 62GB → ใช้ RAM + CPU ช่วย |\n\n## 💡 สรุป:\n\n```\nGPU → คำนวฯ่ส่วนที่พอ\nCPU → คำนวณ experts ที่เหลือ\n\n= Hybrid approach (GPU + CPU ร่วมกัน)\n```\n\nถ้ามี **RTX 4090 24GB** → ไม่ต้องใช้ CPU ช่วย ได้ 40-60 tok/s เต็ม ๆ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":594,"cacheRead":105191,"cacheWrite":959,"totalTokens":106914,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778176153111,"responseId":"064c039b1e952d9b0685980421725580"}}
