{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1060942816\",\n  \"message_id\": \"6907\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"sender\": \"▫️\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-08 01:00 GMT+7\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"▫️ (1060942816)\",\n  \"id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"name\": \"▫️\",\n  \"username\": \"robberzaz\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"d31035dd","parentId":"1c65100f","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:00:15.226Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"57230480","parentId":"d31035dd","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:00:39.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about local models that can analyze well, and then have MiniMax execute the fixes. So they want a local model as the \"smart analyzer\" and MiniMax as the \"worker/executor.\"\n\nFor a local model to be smarter than MiniMax and good at analysis, we're talking about larger models or models specifically tuned for reasoning. Let me think about what's available locally that would be good for analysis.\n\nThe key constraint is VRAM/RAM. With 28GB RAM and potentially 8GB VRAM, what models could work?\n\nOptions:\n1. **Qwen3 72B** - needs ~150GB for full, but with quantization could work with 24GB+ VRAM\n\n\n2. **DeepSeek V3** - ~270B parameters, needs significant VRAM even quantized\n3. **Llama 4 109B** - MoE, could work with less VRAM\n4. **Mistral Small** - 22B, more reasonable requirements\n5. **Qwen2.5 72B** - needs ~150GB, not realistic for this setup\n\nActually, for truly smart analysis that rivals frontier models, I'd really need a 100B+ parameter model, which is impractical for local hardware at this VRAM level. Even with aggressive quantization like Q4_K_M, a 72B model would still require around 45GB just to load, which exceeds what's available here.\n\nThe realistic options that could work for a local setup would be quantized versions of Qwen2.5 72B around 48GB, DeepSeek V2.5 ~110B in 4-bit requiring roughly 60GB, or potentially Llama 4 if it supports MoE. But honestly, with these hardware constraints, MiniMax M2.7 running on a server is probably going to outperform most local alternatives for complex analysis work.\n\nThat said, if the user wants to go the local route, the best approach would be a smaller model specialized for reasoning like Qwen2.5 7B or 14B for quick analysis paired with a larger model for deeper reasoning, or DeepSeek R1 7B for chain-of-thought reasoning, though all of these have significant tradeoffs in capability versus what a server-hosted MiniMax could provide.","thinkingSignature":"51979533b27b12a5f5744921886591dad0a9d43622474233862a973d8cbcbc97"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🤖 Local Models ที่ฉลาด (สำหรับ VRAM 8GB + RAM 28GB)\n\n### ตัวเลือก:\n\n| โมเดล | ขนาด | VRAM ที่ต้องการ | ฉลาดแค่ไหน |\n|--------|-------|------------------|-------------|\n| **Qwen2.5 7B** | 7B | ~6GB (Q4) | ⭐⭐ | \n| **DeepSeek R1 7B** | 7B | ~6GB (Q4) | ⭐⭐⭐ Reasoning เก่ง |\n| **Qwen2.5 14B** | 14B | ~12GB (Q4) | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **Qwen2.5 32B** | 32B | ~20GB (Q4) | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **Qwen3.6 35B** | 35B MoE | ~19GB (Q4) | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n\n### ⚠️ ปัญหา:\n\n**Local model ที่ฉลาดจริง ๆ ต้อง 70B+** — ซึ่งต้องการ VRAM 40GB+\n\n### 💡 ทางออก:\n\n```\nLocal (ฉลาดน้อย) → วิเคราะห์คร่าว ๆ\n        ↓\nMiniMax (ฉลาดกว่า) → แก้จริง ๆ\n```\n\n**แบบนี้ก็ทำได้ แต่...**\n\n### 🔴 ความจริง:\n\n| Local 7B | MiniMax M2.7 |\n|----------|--------------|\n| ฉลาดน้อย | ฉลาดกว่าเยอะ |\n| เร็ว (本地) | เร็ว (server) |\n\n**ไม่มี local model ใดที่ฉลาดกว่า MiniMax แล้วรันได้ใน 8GB VRAM**\n\n### 🎯 สรุป:\n\n```\nต้องการ local ฉลาดจริง ๆ → ต้องมี VRAM 24GB+ ขึ้นไป (RTX 4090)\nไม่งั้น MiniMax ก็ฉลาดกว่าอยู่แล้ว\n```\n\nไม่คุ้มครับเจ้านาย 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":1097,"cacheRead":108927,"cacheWrite":765,"totalTokens":110959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778176815226,"responseId":"064c0632bcf5bc2059a81e1f6617ed1c"}}
