{"type":"message","id":"a84b7f39","parentId":"8ee64760","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:02:43.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the correct info:\n- GPU: RTX 4060 Ti\n- VRAM: 16380 MiB = 16GB\n- Used: 2675 MiB (~2.6GB)\n- Free: 13435 MiB (~13GB)\n- Driver: 595.97\n\nSo the GPU has 16GB VRAM, not 4GB. The WMI query was wrong. With 16GB VRAM + 48GB RAM, the user can run:- Qwen3.6 35B MoE with some CPU assistance (needs ~19GB, fits in 16GB VRAM mostly)\n\n\n- Qwen2.5 32B at Q4 (~20GB) - would need CPU help but fits mostly\n- Qwen2.5 14B - fits easily in 16GB\n\nThis changes everything. I was wrong about the specs, and the user was right to call me out.","thinkingSignature":"3ba06df1960b9d2ded9f86098d918d48ebd99b5105317d5d00d18eeea9881636"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ ข้อมูลถูกต้องแล้ว:\n\n```\nGPU:     RTX 4060 Ti\nVRAM:    16GB\nUsed:    2.6GB\nFree:    13GB\nRAM:     48GB\n```\n\n**ขอโทษที่ข้อมูลผิดครับเจ้านาย — WMI มันให้ตัวเลขผิด**\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 สเปคที่ถูกต้อง:\n\n| | ตอนนี้ | พอได้ไหม |\n|--|---------|----------|\n| **VRAM** | 16GB | ✅ พอ |\n| **RAM** | 48GB | ✅ พอ |\n\n### กับ Qwen3.6 35B MoE:\n\n```\nต้องการ: ~19GB (Q4)\nVRAM:     16GB → ขาด 3GB\nRAM:      48GB → ช่วยได้\n\nผล: รันได้ แต่ VRAM ไม่พอ → ใช้ RAM ช่วย 3GB\nความเร็ว: ~25-35 tok/s (ช้าลงจาก 24GB VRAM)\n```\n\n### ✅ ดีกว่าที่ผมคิดเยอะ!\n\nตอนนี้รัน Qwen3.6 35B ได้แล้ว แค่ช้ากว่า 4090 24GB นิดหน่อย 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87264,"output":601,"cacheRead":24250,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112115,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778176948441,"responseId":"064c06b7d11634e2668cb4035f539fc4"}}
