{"type":"message","id":"82f25b16","parentId":"62c271d0","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:06:48.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a model as smart as DeepSeek. Let me search for what DeepSeek models are available and which ones could run on their 16GB VRAM setup.\n\nDeepSeek V4 Pro is very smart but requires a lot of VRAM. Let me think about what local options are close to DeepSeek's intelligence level.\n\nFrom what I know:\n- DeepSeek V4 Pro/V4 Flash are server models, not local\n- DeepSeek Coder V2 models exist\n\nLet me search for DeepSeek local models that could run on 16GB VRAM.","thinkingSignature":"733b6a1bdd3102b4fba2ff14989d53981274a720764e73c596282cd23a649962"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tfuj3bvsf0yc_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"DeepSeek V4 Pro local GGUF model 16GB VRAM requirements"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":157,"cacheRead":111841,"cacheWrite":4284,"totalTokens":116452,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778177200026,"responseId":"064c07b2afa36b64e440b3ae6d084c38"}}
