{"type":"message","id":"28c7d1d6","parentId":"45596b58","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:08:27.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying that they meant \"smart/intelligent level\" - comparing the intelligence/capability of local models vs DeepSeek V4 Pro. They want a local model that has comparable intelligence to DeepSeek V4 Pro.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The question is: what local model is as smart as DeepSeek V4 Pro?\n\nDeepSeek V4 Pro is a frontier-level model. The question is what local model approaches that level of intelligence.\n\nFor 16GB VRAM, the candidates are:\n- Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B (MoE) - most capable for coding\n- Qwen2.5-Coder-32B - decent but older\n\n\n- The reality is that DeepSeek V4 Pro's 1.6T total parameters (49B active) is vastly larger than what fits on a 16GB card - even Qwen3.6-40B would struggle, and the 35B MoE variant is more comparable to Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B in terms of actual compute. So I'm looking at roughly equivalent local models for 16GB, but none of them truly match DeepSeek V4 Pro's frontier-level intelligence.","thinkingSignature":"a18e7b6a8a2a370bc713f8e1bc321fdf0a668fae391ec4d8e73e5145c236c4b8"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🤔 ความฉลาด DeepSeek V4 Pro อยู่ระดับไหน?\n\nDeepSeek V4 Pro = **Frontier level** (เทียบ GPT-4.5/Claude 4.5)\n\n### Local model ที่ฉลาดที่สุดใน 16GB VRAM:\n\n| โมเดล | ระดับ | ใกล้เคียง |\n|--------|--------|-------------|\n| **Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | DeepSeek Coder V2 Pro |\n| Qwen2.5-Coder-32B | ⭐⭐⭐ | GPT-4 เก่า |\n| DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite 16B | ⭐⭐⭐ | GPT-3.5 Turbo |\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 ความจริง:\n\n**ไม่มี local model ใน 16GB VRAM ที่ฉลาดเทียบ DeepSeek V4 Pro ได้**\n\nเพราะ:\n- DeepSeek V4 Pro = 1.6T params (frontier)\n- Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B = 31B params (compact)\n\n---\n\n## 💡 ทางออก:\n\n| ถ้าต้องการ | วิธี |\n|-------------|-------|\n| ฉลาดจริง ๆ | ใช้ DeepSeek API / MiniMax |\n| Local + ฉลาด | ต้อง 24GB+ VRAM (RTX 4090) |\n| Local ดีที่สุดใน 16GB | Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B |\n\n**สรุป:** Local + DeepSeek level = ต้อง RTX 4090 ขึ้นไปครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":699,"cacheRead":115988,"cacheWrite":3019,"totalTokens":119876,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177289383,"responseId":"064c080c70cee687c939bd3677605542"}}
