e-train DeepSeek - V3 on 14.8 trillion diverse and high-quality tokens, followed by Supervised Fine-Tuning and Reinforcement Learning stages to fully harness its capabilities.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d5d6c07e45514baa\">>>","siteName":"www.modelscope.cn"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778177446129}}
{"type":"message","id":"f35eb9c8","parentId":"d4c201ff","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:10:59.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. Let me compile the results for models that can run on 16GB VRAM and are close to DeepSeek intelligence:\n\n1. **DeepSeek-Coder-V3 (Distilled)** - 12GB VRAM, 40.5% SWE-bench, best quality-per-GB\n2. **Codestral 25.12** - 16GB VRAM, best for fast inline code completion\n3. **Gemma 4 26B A4B** - fast by tokens/s\n4. **Mistral Large 3** - with quantization, can run on limited VRAM\n5. **DeepSeek-V3.2** - 24GB VRAM (needs quantization), leads on reasoning\n\nFor 16GB VRAM specifically:\n\n\n- DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled: 12GB ✅\n- Codestral 25.12: 16GB ✅\n- Gemma 4 26B A4B: ?\n- Mistral Large 3: needs quantization\n\nDeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled stands out as the best quality-per-GB option for this VRAM constraint, though it's worth noting this is the distilled version rather than the full model.","thinkingSignature":"6c0fd6cb097743fbaf185411dd381f9a450e6196fb9720c4cbc01b030f1ecb1e"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ มีตัวที่ใกล้เคียง!\n\nจากข้อมูลล่าสุด สรุปให้:\n\n### 🏆 ดีที่สุดใน 16GB VRAM:\n\n| โมเดล | VRAM | SWE-bench | หมายเหตุ |\n|--------|------|-----------|-----------|\n| **DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled** | **12GB** | **40.5%** | ⭐ Best quality-per-GB |\n| Codestral 25.12 | 16GB | ? | Fast code completion |\n| Gemma 4 26B A4B | ? | ? | เร็วที่สุด |\n| Mistral Large 3 | 16GB (INT8) | ? | ต้อง quantize |\n\n### 💡 DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled:\n\n```\n- 12GB VRAM (พอดีกับ 16GB)\n- SWE-bench: 40.5%\n- ฉลาดระดับ DeepSeek\n- ออกแบบมาเพื่อ coding โดยเฉพาะ\n```\n\n### 📊 เทียบ:\n\n| โมเดล | SWE-bench | VRAM |\n|--------|-----------|------|\n| DeepSeek V4 Pro (API) | ~60% | Server |\n| **DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled** | **40.5%** | **12GB** |\n| Qwen3-Coder-30B | ~35% | 19GB |\n\n---\n\n**DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled = ทางเลือกที่ดีที่สุดใน 16GB VRAM** ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102607,"output":678,"cacheRead":24250,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177446132,"responseId":"064c08a866c548324433e6e03553c331"}}
