{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1060942816\",\n  \"message_id\": \"6937\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"sender\": \"▫️\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-08 01:12 GMT+7\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"▫️ (1060942816)\",\n  \"id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"name\": \"▫️\",\n  \"username\": \"robberzaz\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"801f4eb0","parentId":"8a7ec751","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:12:07.268Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"fbea8966","parentId":"801f4eb0","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:12:24.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled can solve problems well (specifically coding problems). Let me think about this...\n\nSWE-bench 40.5% means it can solve about 40% of real software engineering problems from GitHub. But the user is asking about \"แก้ปัญหา\" (solving problems) in general.\n\nLet me be honest - SWE-bench measures how well a model can resolve real GitHub issues. 40.5% is decent but not great. It's better than most local models in 12GB VRAM, but it's not at the level of DeepSeek V4 Pro or GPT-4.\n\nAlso, the user's actual use case matters - are they doing:\n1. Code completion (autocomplete) → Codestral might be better\n2. Debugging → DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled is good\n3. Complex problem solving → needs more capable model\n\nLet me give an honest assessment.","thinkingSignature":"106ab346f0454aeec7f5c04ca883467d6646aa94bd7e9ee388264fa3e826e41e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🧠 ตอบตรง ๆ:\n\n**SWE-bench 40.5% = แก้ปัญหาได้ประมาณ 40% ของปัญหาจริงบน GitHub**\n\n### ความหมาย:\n\n| ระดับ | พร้อมแก้ |\n|--------|------------|\n| **ง่าย** (bug ทั่วไป) | ✅ ได้ดี |\n| **กลาง** (refactor, optimize) | ✅ ได้ดี |\n| **ยาก** (architect, complex debugging) | ⚠️ ได้บ้าง |\n| **สุดยาก** (คิด algorithm ซับซ้อน) | ❌ ยังไม่ค่อยได้ |\n\n### 📊 ความจริง:\n\n```\nDeepSeek V4 Pro (API)  → 60%+  SWE-bench  → แก้ปัญหายากได้ดี\nDeepSeek-Coder-V3 Dist → 40.5%             → แก้ได้ระดับกลาง\nQwen3-Coder-30B        → ~35%               → แก้ได้ระดับพื้นฐาน\n```\n\n### 🎯 สรุป:\n\n**DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled แก้ปัญหาระดับพื้นฐาน-กลางได้ดี**\n**แต่ปัญหายาก ๆ → ยังต้องใช้ API (DeepSeek/MiniMax)**\n\nถ้าต้องการ**แก้ทุกปัญหาได้เก่ง ๆ** → ต้อง API อยู่ดีครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":686,"cacheRead":119346,"cacheWrite":7396,"totalTokens":127598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177527268,"responseId":"064c08fa70cbe6620a3134d986c04050"}}
