{"type":"message","id":"4d646002","parentId":"4681e93a","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:16:48.564Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking which local model to use for coding that's smart enough, given their computer specs:\n- GPU: RTX 4060 Ti 16GB VRAM\n- RAM: 48GB\n- CPU: AMD Ryzen 5 3500X 6-Core\n\nThey want a local model that's smart enough for coding tasks. Let me give them the best recommendation for their hardware.\n\nFrom what we discussed earlier:\n- Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B: ~19GB (might fit with some offloading)\n- DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled: 12GB - fits well\n\n\n- Qwen2.5-Coder-32B: ~20GB Q4\n\nWith 16GB VRAM and 48GB RAM, the best option would be Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B since the MoE architecture lets it potentially run with CPU offloading for the rest. Alternatively, DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled at 12GB would fit more comfortably and still delivers solid coding performance.","thinkingSignature":"b286b062beeada8c38332bbe1f594990530678fe4efa44a4074a1e7f0c86eec7"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🤖 สเปคเจ้าของ (RTX 4060 Ti 16GB VRAM + 48GB RAM)\n\n### 🏆 แนะนำ:\n\n| โมเดล | VRAM | RAM | ฉลาด |\n|--------|------|-----|-------|\n| **Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B** | ~16GB | 48GB ✅ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **DeepSeek-Coder-V3 Distilled** | ~12GB | 48GB ✅ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n\n### ⭐ ตัวเลือกที่ดีที่สุด:\n\n**Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B (MoE)**\n```\n- 31B params แต่ใช้ ~19GB Q4\n- VRAM 16GB = โหลด GPU ได้เกือบหมด\n- RAM 48GB = ช่วย offload ส่วนที่เหลือ\n- SWE-bench: ~35-40%\n- ฉลาดระดับกลาง-สูง\n```\n\n### ⚙️ วิธีรัน:\n\n```bash\n# ใช้ llama.cpp\n--ctx-size 66560\n--batch-size 2048\n--ubatch-size 512\n--cache-type-k q4_0\n--cache-type-v q4_0\n--flash-attn on\n--cont-batching\n--mlock\n--n-gpu-layers 999\n--n-cpu-moe 38\n```\n\n### 📊 เทียบกับ API:\n\n| | Local Qwen3-Coder-30B | MiniMax API |\n|--|------------------------|-------------|\n| **ฉลาด** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **ความเร็ว** | 25-35 tok/s | 50-100 tok/s |\n| **ค่าใช้จ่าย** | ครั้งเดียว | $10/เดือน |\n| **Privacy** | ✅ 100% | ❌ |\n\n**สรุป:** Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B คุ้มค่าที่สุดสำหรับ 16GB VRAM ครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":772,"cacheRead":132452,"cacheWrite":4181,"totalTokens":137575,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177792877,"responseId":"064c0a04ae0621d9bb2c6db41f5f3702"}}
