{"type":"message","id":"7ce26406","parentId":"949ecb5e","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:17:32.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking to compare Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B (local) vs MiniMax API for coding tasks. They want a direct comparison specifically for writing code.","thinkingSignature":"45b437fb162f10882e8e8cc4b5c85cd75de7307c227506caca711eb171172332"},{"type":"text","text":"## ⚖️ Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B (Local) vs MiniMax API\n\n| | Local Qwen3-Coder-30B | MiniMax |\n|--|------------------------|---------|\n| **เขียนโค้ด** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **ความเร็ว** | 25-35 tok/s | 50-100 tok/s |\n| **ตั้งค่า** | ยุ่งยาก | พร้อมใช้ |\n| **ค่าใช้จ่าย** | ฮาร์ดแวร์ + ไฟฟ้า | $10/เดือน |\n| **Privacy** | ✅ | ❌ |\n| **ต้องรอ setup** | ✅ | ❌ |\n\n### 🎯 สรุป:\n\n```\nถ้าแค่เขียนโค้ด = MiniMax พอแล้ว\nถ้าอยาก local + ฉลาด = Qwen3-Coder-30B คุ้ม\n```\n\n**ไม่ต่างกันมากเรื่องความฉลาด** — แต่ MiniMax สะดวกกว่าเยอะ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":362,"cacheRead":137081,"cacheWrite":477,"totalTokens":138090,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177841695,"responseId":"064c0a35fdc361e6075699718c4469b6"}}
