{"type":"message","id":"bc25e400","parentId":"f7b75a7d","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:18:42.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking specifically about intelligence/smartness comparison between Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B (Local) vs MiniMax. Let me be honest about this.","thinkingSignature":"88b9da7a7b07afbcf7987c298ac68a70830aec51dd4349843ee01f0a733ee77b"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🧠 ความฉลาด — เทียบตรง ๆ:\n\n| | Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B | MiniMax M2.7 |\n|--|------------------------|---------------|\n| **เข้าใจปัญหา** | ⭐⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **วิเคราะห์โค้ด** | ⭐⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **แก้ bug ซับซ้อน** | ⭐⭐⭐ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **context เยอะ** | 64K | 1M+ |\n\n### 🔴 ความจริง:\n\n```\nQwen3-Coder-30B = โมเดลเล็ก (30B)\nMiniMax M2.7     = โมเดลใหญ่กว่า\n\nMiniMax ฉลาดกว่าเกือบทุกด้าน\n```\n\n### 💡 สรุป:\n\n| ถ้าต้องการ | ตัวไหน |\n|-------------|---------|\n| ฉลาดสุด | **MiniMax** |\n| local + ดีที่สุด | Qwen3-Coder-30B |\n\n**MiniMax ยังฉลาดกว่าอยู่ดี** 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":384,"cacheRead":137421,"cacheWrite":487,"totalTokens":138462,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177910834,"responseId":"064c0a7bf001500015c86fa4dd7c0b85"}}
