{"type":"message","id":"285642e4","parentId":"14df8347","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:19:37.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying - they just want a model that's smart enough for coding, not the absolute best at everything. They're asking if Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B is good enough for just coding without being stupid.\n\nLet me give a direct answer - Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B is more than capable for coding tasks. It's designed specifically for coding and is very competent.","thinkingSignature":"e52a8d642e22cf075292bf9dfcefd840d9964f4b06df7ecd7840dde83fbda7f0"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B — พอแล้ว!\n\n```\nเขียนโค้ดไม่โง่ = ✅ Qwen3-Coder-30B ทำได้สบาย\n```\n\n### เหตุผล:\n\n```\n- ออกแบบมาเพื่อ coding โดยเฉพาะ\n- 30B params = ฉลาดพอสำหรับโค้ดส่วนใหญ่\n- ไม่ใช่โมเดลโง่\n```\n\n### 🎯 สรุป:\n\n**Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B เพียงพอสำหรับเขียนโค้ดที่ไม่โง่** \n\nถ้าต้องการแค่นี้ → **พอแล้ว** 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":321,"cacheRead":137771,"cacheWrite":525,"totalTokens":138787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778177969101,"responseId":"064c0ab4eb84aee04e5302831fa5ff76"}}
