go.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a7d45a69f04acb88\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline Review (2026): VS Code Agent for Real Multi-Step Coding\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a7d45a69f04acb88\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://vibecoding.app/blog/cline-review\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"23ab358aaba569a2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline is a VS Code -first coding agent that can read files, propose edits, run terminal commands, and test flows with browser automation. It is one of the strongest options if you want autonomous task execution without leaving your editor. Real strength: multi-step implementation with approval gates and clear diff review . Real tradeoff: token costs and occasional overreach on architecture changes.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"23ab358aaba569a2\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"vibecoding.app\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3cc56a93cf67f16a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline Review 2026: The Open-Source AI Coding Agent Taking Over VS Code\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3cc56a93cf67f16a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://hubpy.io/blog/cline-guide-2026\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"84d87307f5b9e107\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat Is Cline ? Cline (formerly Claude Dev) is an open-source VS Code extension that turns your editor into an autonomous AI coding environment. Unlike traditional autocomplete tools, Cline can independently create and edit files, execute terminal commands, and even control a browser — while asking for your approval at each step.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"84d87307f5b9e107\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"hubpy.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8e8b55eaf6341064\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline AI Review: VS Code AI Agent Performance & Pricing | archgen.dev\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8e8b55eaf6341064\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.archgen.dev/blog/cline-ai-review-vs-code-ai-agent\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2f5f0bddefcc5224\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline AI is a VS Code extension that functions as an autonomous AI coding agent . Unlike traditional code completion tools that offer suggestions as you type, Cline can perform complete tasks, understand project context, and even interact with your terminal and file system.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2f5f0bddefcc5224\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.archgen.dev\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e8591038bf6fb5f6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline Review 2026 | ToolChase\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e8591038bf6fb5f6\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://toolchase.com/tool/cline/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3a535b29e1fd0486\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCline review 2026 : Open-source AI coding assistant for VS Code with multi-model support. Free to use. See features, setup, and alternatives.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3a535b29e1fd0486\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"toolchase.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Cline VS Code extension AI coding agent 2026 review","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":977,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1fa9da859b24a9ce\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGLM-5.1: Top-Tier AI Coding - Coding Plan: GLM-5.1 access\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1fa9da859b24a9ce\">>>","url":"https://duckduckgo.com/y.js?ad_domain=byteplus.com&ad_provider=bingv7aa&ad_type=txad&click_metadata=XGZ6LkVT0oA%2DGom7Hz%2D6IPxLjxlCv1FB5dSGNAmS9aA__1MhsIALz53NVcXYbgsi93anIE30aKVpAIufC5jGpye