n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3cc56a93cf67f16a\">>>","url":"https://hubpy.io/blog/cline-guide-2026","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"84d87307f5b9e107\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhat Is Cline ? Cline (formerly Claude Dev) is an open-source VS Code extension that turns your editor into an autonomous AI coding environment. Unlike traditional autocomplete tools, Cline can independently create and edit files, execute terminal commands, and even control a browser — while asking for your approval at each step.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"84d87307f5b9e107\">>>","siteName":"hubpy.io"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8e8b55eaf6341064\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCline AI Review: VS Code AI Agent Performance & Pricing | archgen.dev\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8e8b55eaf6341064\">>>","url":"https://www.archgen.dev/blog/cline-ai-review-vs-code-ai-agent","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2f5f0bddefcc5224\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCline AI is a VS Code extension that functions as an autonomous AI coding agent . Unlike traditional code completion tools that offer suggestions as you type, Cline can perform complete tasks, understand project context, and even interact with your terminal and file system.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2f5f0bddefcc5224\">>>","siteName":"www.archgen.dev"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e8591038bf6fb5f6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCline Review 2026 | ToolChase\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e8591038bf6fb5f6\">>>","url":"https://toolchase.com/tool/cline/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3a535b29e1fd0486\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCline review 2026 : Open-source AI coding assistant for VS Code with multi-model support. Free to use. See features, setup, and alternatives.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3a535b29e1fd0486\">>>","siteName":"toolchase.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778178595257}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c430ae5","parentId":"8adf3615","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:30:08.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found good info about Cline. Let me summarize.","thinkingSignature":"bf42047587109caccc4ee1d49a79e42d438f4c3a3d34986d19fb5a1ddbb58908"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🤖 Cline — VS Code Extension\n\n### ✅ ดี:\n\n| ฟีเจอร์ | รายละเอียด |\n|----------|-------------|\n| **Autonomous** | อ่านไฟล์, แก้ไข, รันคำสั่งเอง |\n| **Multi-model** | ใช้ได้หลายโมเดล (Claude, GPT, etc.) |\n| **Approval gates** | ถามก่อนทำทุกขั้นตอน |\n| **Open source** | ฟรี |\n| **Diff review** | ดูการเปลี่ยนแก่นก่อน approve |\n\n### ⚠️ ต้องระวัง:\n\n| ปัญหา | รายละเอียด |\n|--------|-------------|\n| Token costs | ใช้ API → เสียตาม usage |\n| Overreach | บางทีแก้ architecture เกิน |\n| ไม่เสถียร | บางครั้งทำผิด |\n\n### 🔄 เทียบกับ Cursor:\n\n| | Cline | Cursor |\n|--|--------|--------|\n| ราคา | ฟรี (แต่เสีย API) | $20/เดือน |\n| Model | หลายตัว | ตัวเดียว |\n| UI | VS Code | VS Code fork |\n\n### 🎯 สรุป:\n\n**Cline ดีถ้า:**\n- อยากใช้หลายโมเดล (Claude, GPT, etc.)\n- ชอบ VS Code อยู่แล้ว\n- อยาก approve ทุกขั้นตอน\n\n**Cursor ดีกว่าถ้า:**\n- อยากได้ UI ลื่นกว่า\n- Tab completion เด็ดขาด 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117276,"output":522,"cacheRead":24250,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778178595261,"responseId":"064c0d242492cd36f1edf28398e7728b"}}
