{"type":"message","id":"67519ce4","parentId":"02589751","timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:42:43.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"VS Code isn't found via `code` command. It might not be installed in WSL. The user is on Windows. I should guide them to install it directly in Windows.\n\nThe best way is to just tell them to open VS Code and install from the Extension marketplace, or give them the VSIX download link.\n\nLet me give them the simple instructions.","thinkingSignature":"7204a6296d77ffb885a767ec1ec13eda7e9a88ec4b2dc6b069eed81207ec8840"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📦 วิธีลง Cline:\n\n**ทาง 1 — VS Code (แนะนำ):**\n1. เปิด VS Code\n2. กด `Ctrl+Shift+X` เปิด Extensions\n3. พิมพ์ `Cline`\n4. กด **Install**\n\n**ทาง 2 — ลิงก์ตรง:**\n```\nhttps://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=saoudrizwan.claude-dev\n```\n\n**ทาง 3 — GitHub:**\n```\nhttps://github.com/cline/cline/releases\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔑 หลังลงเสร็จ:\n\n1. เปิด Cline (กด `Ctrl+Shift+P` → พิมพ์ `Cline`)\n2. ใส่ API key (Claude / OpenAI / etc.)\n3. เปิดโปรเจกต์ที่อยากให้มันทำงาน\n4. พิมพ์ task แล้วกด Enter\n\n**ลงเสร็จบอกได้เลยครับ** 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119302,"output":360,"cacheRead":24250,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143912,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778179353094,"responseId":"064c101bbdfd138e1e2d04e37f4df70d"}}
